{
  "stem": "17606.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Also, and who was in charge of the political department the Jewish military organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let me just-- just step aside for one second.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I'm talking mostly about the Jewish military organizations, in no way I want to undermine the brave people of the Jewish community organization.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were brave boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I talk about the Jewish military, because I was with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I know the best what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By no means I want to undermine the other group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were just as brave as my-- as my group, maybe even braver.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It cannot be measured, bravery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was in charge of the political department, Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], who later on led the revolt in-- in this-- in Trawniki when he was caught, he and-- and David-- what is his name, I'll remind myself later-- led the revolt in Trawniki.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [INAUDIBLE] told us they escape from the transport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they tell us that the train master saw the train operators told them that if train is going to Treblinka then Treblinka is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They are being shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And now, they are building a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that, that's when the [INAUDIBLE] come out and the revenge group started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they told me, I believed them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I knew them very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were kids with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the first information we got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know when they military-- the [NON-ENGLISH], the Jewish fighting organization got it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, we could talk--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We We could talk to-- yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we-- we posted that information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we shared that [INAUDIBLE] that information with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although, that group was information only at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
